      <title>Sasha</title>
      <author>spicyBeefu</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/541083</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/541083#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">f333067e0f6d0664b464090e91efccebc2eeb662</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 00:47:11 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66de442a8460c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66de442f808f3.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;Finished port of Sasha to AC:NL! If you notice anything that seems off, please lmk in Twitter DMs.&lt;br&gt;Furniture was fairly half-assed because I didn't want to spend more than 2 full days making this. If anyone wants to make changes I'll gladly update the file if it's better!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Replaces Gaston (rbt04), changes motto, catchphrase, house exterior, interior, style tastes, portrait, personality, just about anything I could get at with the limited documentation. I don't play New Leaf much right now so I've been unable to test thoroughly outside of making sure the house and talking doesn't crash, use at your own risk!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Should crash your game without NL version 1.5 update, so make sure you get that first b4 loading mods.&lt;br&gt;Tested on USA copy of the game, not certain about other region compatibility. Gaston amiibo card will get them into your town easily! Save editors might not put correct furniture in the house.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;For anyone else making custom villagers, I've filled out a bunch of unknown variables in the 010 Editor template file you can find in the tutorials. I bundled my edited one in here with Sasha. Apologies in advance if any errors.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;See installation instructions for game mods for Emulator or real 3DS on google!</description>
